---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/?$/, '/');
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Raz Cohen"
  description="Product designer and design leader focused on defining problems before solving them. View portfolio and connect."
  activePage="about"
>
  <section class="about-section">
    <img
      src={`${base}images/Raz.jpg`}
      alt="Raz Cohen"
      class="about-photo"
      loading="eager"
    />
    <div class="about-text">
      <h1 class="about-heading">
        I'm a product designer and design leader. I believe every great solution
        starts with properly defining the problem.
      </h1>
      <p class="about-para">
        Today I work with startups — including Tedooo, Bookaway, Axel and FINQ —
        as a product designer and consultant: leading product projects, building
        design systems, mentoring designers and structuring AI-assisted design
        workflows. I also teach in the Visual Communication program at Shenkar —
        Emotional Design, App Design and Interaction Design — and mentor students
        through their graduation projects.
      </p>
      <p class="about-para">
        Before going independent, I spent eight years at Fiverr, the last four as
        Director of Product Design, leading a 25-person group of team leaders,
        product designers and UX researchers. Along the way I made the case for
        and established Fiverr's UX research function, initiated its design
        system, and built the design processes, roles and growth paths the team
        worked by.
      </p>
      <p class="about-para">
        Earlier, I was a UX/UI designer at Hola and a motion designer at
        Promotheus. I graduated from Shenkar's Visual Communication department
        in 2010 — the same program I teach in today.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Ft0MpG9xpo4Y0GhZ_aa0gSpFQxy4yWYL/view?usp=sharing"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="about-cv-btn"
      >View my CV</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
